==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiān bù cóng rén yuàn
===Proverb===
'''[[天]][[不]][[从]][[人]][[愿]]'''
# Heaven does not abide by the wishes of people.
===Alternate forms===
[[天不從人願]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
